    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Essential oil distilled from species of Cymbopogon grass, and used as a stabilizer in soaps, perfumes, and cosmetics. It contains 70–80 percent citral, which may be isolated by distillation or from the oils of verbena and citronella. </Note_Text>
